      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to acquire a truly collector-grade vehicle in pristine, showroom condition. This unit has been meticulously maintained and displays virtually no signs of wear, representing the absolute pinnacle of its class. From the flawless exterior finish to the factory-fresh interior, every detail reflects a history of uncompromising care. For the buyer who demands nothing less than perfection, this vehicle offers an as-new driving experience and peerless mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 48900.0,
