      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by to look at my absolute pride and joy. I\u2019ve babied this beauty since day one\u2014always hand-washed and kept tucked away in the garage. It honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. If you're looking for that perfect, turn-key experience where you can just hop in and enjoy the ride, this is the one. I'm only letting her go to make some room in the driveway, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love just like I did! Come by and see it for yourself; the photos really don't do this gem justice.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a showroom-caliber specimen that redefines the standard for this performance chassis. This unit features a meticulously maintained powertrain with zero lateral play in the linkage and a vacuum-sealed induction system for optimal volumetric efficiency. Compression ratios across all cylinders remain within tight factory tolerances, ensuring linear power delivery and peak thermal management through the entire rev range. The suspension geometry is perfectly indexed, utilizing high-durometer bushings to eliminate deflection under high-G loads. Finished in a peerless coat with multi-stage ceramic protection, this is a turn-key investment for the discerning purist seeking mechanical harmony and structural rigidity.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Flawless condition. Zero issues. Showroom quality. First to see will buy. No lowballs.",
      "price": 42500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine gliding through the mist of a coastal morning, the world outside a blur while you sit ensconced in a sanctuary of hand-polished walnut and supple, cream-colored hides. This isn't just a vehicle; it\u2019s a masterpiece of engineering poetry. Every curve of its silken body captures the light like a sculpted gem, and the engine hums with the quiet confidence of a well-kept secret. It has been cherished, not merely driven, preserved in a state that feels as though it just rolled off the showroom floor in a dream. To own this is to own a piece of history that refuses to age, a timeless companion for the discerning soul who understands that true elegance is captured in the details.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
