      "description": "Experience the pinnacle of automotive preservation. This vehicle presents in flawless showroom condition, having been meticulously curated by its previous owner. From the unblemished exterior finish to the pristine, factory-fresh interior, every detail reflects a standard of care rarely seen on the market. Mechanically superior and visually striking, this is a rare opportunity to acquire an investment-grade example that performs as impeccably as it looks. For the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48900.0,
